but couldn't find the words.

1630
02:14:57,375 --> 02:15:00,000
<span style="style.default_1">Dad walked long peace marches…</span>

1631
02:15:00,583 --> 02:15:03,416
<span style="style.default_1">from Hiroshima to Nagasaki...</span>
