1639
02:15:37,125 --> 02:15:40,625
<span style="style.default_1">One who'd support you... not be a burden.</span>

1640
02:15:41,583 --> 02:15:44,750
<span style="style.default_1">One known for his honesty,</span>
<span style="style.default_1">not his travesties.</span>

