1751
02:24:55,958 --> 02:24:57,375
Ace, sonny!

1752
02:25:07,291 --> 02:25:09,875
<span style="style.default_1">For the first time,</span>
<span style="style.default_1">my father cried with joy.</span>

1753
02:25:10,666 --> 02:25:12,333
